description: Demolition of existing building and construction of two blocks of flats, one 3-8 storeys in height comprising 50 flats and the other part 4 and part 5 storeys in height comprising 18 affordable flats, alterations to access, underground parking for 43 cars and outdoor amenity space (variation to scheme approved 21 March 2003 ref 01-1655 for 59 flats).
